content.text:
### `PageHeader` in `@procertus-ui/ui-lib`
New presentational building blocks under `packages/ui-lib/src/components/page-header/`:

- **`PageHeader`** — props: `kicker`, `title`, `description`, `media`, `actions`, plus normal **`header`** attributes (via `Omit<ComponentProps<"header">, "title">` so `title` is your main heading slot, not the HTML tooltip attribute). Plain **string/number** `kicker` / `description` / `title` get default typography (`PageHeaderKicker`, `PageHeaderDescription`, **`H1`** for title).
- **Slot primitives** (same layout tokens when composing by hand): **`PageHeaderKicker`**, **`PageHeaderDescription`**, **`PageHeaderMedia`**, **`PageHeaderActions`**.

### Storybook
- **`PageHeader.stories.tsx`** — dashboard-style default, title-only, with actions, and a composition example using the slot components.

### Package export
- **`packages/ui-lib/src/index.ts`** — exports `PageHeader`, slot components, and **`PageHeaderProps`**.

### Dashboard app
- **`DashboardPage.tsx`** — uses **`PageHeader`** from **`@procertus-ui/ui-lib`** with the previous welcome copy and logo; **`H1`** still from **`@procertus-ui/ui`** for the main title.
- **Removed** **`DashboardWelcomeWidget.tsx`** and its export from **`dashboard-widgets/index.ts`**.

